1
00:00:09,365 --> 00:00:11,010
Jadi, kau suka dia atau tak?

2
00:00:11,183 --> 00:00:13,758
Belum sampai suka lagi. Cuma nak kenal dia lebih.

3
00:00:14,097 --> 00:00:16,100
Kau rasa Fah tahu itu kau?

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,945
Kalau Typhoon sebenar, dia pun takkan dapat cakap dengan P'Fah.

5
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:22,555
Kau takut kehilangan P'Fah.

6
00:00:23,088 --> 00:00:24,874
Tapi kau tak takut P'Fah jatuh hati pada orang lain?

7
00:00:25,548 --> 00:00:26,582
Mestilah aku takut.

8
00:00:26,848 --> 00:00:30,122
Kenapa dengan kau, Fah? Biasanya kau terima je dari sesiapa, kan?

9
00:00:30,426 --> 00:00:32,274
Sebab sekarang dah ada orang dalam hati dia.

10
00:00:32,539 --> 00:00:34,197
Macam mana dia boleh terima dari orang lain sesuka hati?

11
00:00:34,413 --> 00:00:35,878
Selamat hari jadi.

12
00:00:36,080 --> 00:00:36,924
Terima kasih.

13
00:02:19,691 --> 00:02:22,016
- Selamat pagi, Doktor Fah.
- Selamat pagi.

14
00:02:23,171 --> 00:02:23,761
Nah, ini.

15
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,997
Ini untuk awak.

16
00:02:37,539 --> 00:02:39,019
Selamat hari jadi.

17
00:02:39,502 --> 00:02:41,357
Awak mesti dah dapat banyak ucapan hari jadi.

18
00:02:41,604 --> 00:02:44,392
Tapi izinkan saya jadi seorang lagi yang mendoakan awak.

19
00:02:44,672 --> 00:02:45,914
Sama ada pelajaran awak,

20
00:02:46,137 --> 00:02:47,318
atau kerja awak,

21
00:02:47,499 --> 00:02:48,874
awak memang hebat.

22
00:02:49,602 --> 00:02:51,648
Saya harap awak pun ada masa untuk berehat.

23
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,188
Dan bahagia selalu.

24
00:02:54,016 --> 00:02:57,758
Sebab senyuman awak antara keajaiban dunia.

25
00:02:58,321 --> 00:03:00,602
Saya beli kamera Polaroid sebagai hadiah hari jadi awak.

26
00:03:00,853 --> 00:03:02,611
Kalau tak menyusahkan,

27
00:03:02,914 --> 00:03:04,842
saya nak ajak awak ambil gambar bersama.

28
00:03:05,459 --> 00:03:07,801
Supaya kita boleh kongsi gambar kehidupan harian.

29
00:03:09,285 --> 00:03:11,000
Tapi kalau tak sesuai, tak apa.

30
00:03:12,407 --> 00:03:13,687
Cukup sekadar terima

31
00:03:13,973 --> 00:03:15,374
pun dah buat saya sangat gembira.

32
00:03:29,407 --> 00:03:30,117
Jadi, macam mana?

33
00:03:31,444 --> 00:03:32,395
Mm.

34
00:03:32,945 --> 00:03:33,872
Aku rasa orangnya sama.

35
00:03:38,971 --> 00:03:40,419
Aku rasa aku dah jumpa orang dari surat-surat tu.

36
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:41,900
Tak.

37
00:03:42,656 --> 00:03:43,905
Dia datang jumpa aku sendiri.

38
00:03:45,075 --> 00:03:46,811
Kau tak cam tulisan tangan dia?

39
00:03:48,991 --> 00:03:52,860
Dulu tulisan Phoon bukan macam ni.
Atau dia sengaja ubah supaya aku tak cam?

40
00:03:53,386 --> 00:03:54,962
Tapi lepas menulis lama, dia mesti dah biasa.

41
00:03:55,688 --> 00:03:57,222
Jadi masa tulis kad hari jadi, dia tersasul.

42
00:03:58,591 --> 00:03:59,804
Apa pendapat kau tentang dia?

43
00:04:03,388 --> 00:04:06,282
Dulu aku anggap Phoon cuma macam adik.

44
00:04:07,783 --> 00:04:09,481
Budak sebelah rumah yang aku nak jaga sebaiknya.

45
00:04:10,299 --> 00:04:12,691
Tapi kau tahu dia tak pernah anggap kau sekadar abang.

46
00:04:13,468 --> 00:04:14,376
Aku tahu.

47
00:04:15,671 --> 00:04:17,312
Dan aku pasti Phoon pun tahu.

48
00:04:17,776 --> 00:04:20,337
Tapi lepas semua ni jadi,

49
00:04:20,682 --> 00:04:22,391
rasa macam aku kenal sisi lain Phoon.

50
00:04:23,774 --> 00:04:25,632
Sisi yang bukan sekadar adik kecil macam dulu.

51
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,752
Jadi sekarang kau rasa macam mana tentang dia?

52
00:04:29,955 --> 00:04:31,490
Aku suka orang dari surat-surat tu.

53
00:04:32,922 --> 00:04:34,487
Kalau orang tu Phoon,

54
00:04:36,170 --> 00:04:37,525
maksudnya aku suka Phoon.

55
00:04:38,762 --> 00:04:39,691
Itu je sebenarnya.

56
00:04:40,062 --> 00:04:41,368
Kau tak marah dia?

57
00:04:41,642 --> 00:04:42,985
Sebab tak jujur dengan kau?

58
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:45,577
Aku—

59
00:04:45,911 --> 00:04:46,911
Sebenarnya aku gembira.

60
00:04:47,145 --> 00:04:48,014
Sebab itu Phoon.

61
00:04:48,813 --> 00:04:50,074
Jadi kau nak buat apa sekarang?

62
00:04:50,899 --> 00:04:54,330
Kau nak kekal macam ni dan tunggu dia mengaku?

63
00:04:56,699 --> 00:04:57,893
Aku—

64
00:04:58,235 --> 00:05:00,425
Dulu aku ingat aku cukup sabar untuk tunggu.

65
00:05:01,506 --> 00:05:03,050
Tapi sekarang aku tak pasti lagi.

66
00:05:10,788 --> 00:05:12,494
Kenapa P'Fah baik sangat?

67
00:05:12,952 --> 00:05:14,220
Dia sampai ingat.

68
00:05:14,546 --> 00:05:15,914
Yang aku takut gelap.

69
00:05:17,811 --> 00:05:21,120
Kau pasti boleh mengajar macam ni? Kau memang tak okey.

70
00:05:22,527 --> 00:05:24,309
Sejujurnya aku tak tahu patut buat macam mana.

71
00:05:24,847 --> 00:05:26,014
Buat macam biasa je.

72
00:05:26,871 --> 00:05:28,933
Senyum, bertenang, dan buat macam biasa.

73
00:05:29,152 --> 00:05:30,488
Takkan jadi apa-apa. Kau boleh.

74
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:35,992
Kuatkan diri. Kau akan lepasinya. Percayalah.

75
00:05:37,635 --> 00:05:39,094
- Easter.
- Ya.

76
00:05:39,801 --> 00:05:41,906
Jom pergi sekarang?

77
00:05:42,863 --> 00:05:44,542
Ya, jom.

78
00:05:45,610 --> 00:05:46,300
Phoon macam mana?

79
00:05:47,568 --> 00:05:48,460
Kau ikut sekali?

80
00:05:49,155 --> 00:05:52,364
Oh, korang pergi dulu. Aku kena urus sesuatu dulu.

81
00:05:54,426 --> 00:05:56,524
Phoon, mana pen yang kau pinjam dari aku?

82
00:05:56,952 --> 00:05:58,659
Pen yang aku pinjam? Oh, aku cari dulu.

83
00:05:59,534 --> 00:06:00,773
- Jumpa dah.
- Okey.

84
00:06:02,211 --> 00:06:03,921
Jumpa lagi. Bye.

85
00:06:04,828 --> 00:06:06,093
- Nak yang ni juga?
- Ambil je.

86
00:06:06,145 --> 00:06:07,062
Jom.

87
00:06:08,844 --> 00:06:09,749
Kita tengah berebut makanan ke sekarang?

88
00:06:14,417 --> 00:06:15,739
P’Gib, ini.

89
00:06:16,045 --> 00:06:16,934
Okey.

90
00:06:19,417 --> 00:06:20,958
Hei, jangan pergi dulu.

91
00:06:21,946 --> 00:06:24,459
Doktor Fah suruh saya buat koko untuk orang istimewa.

92
00:06:24,733 --> 00:06:25,891
Tunggu sekejap. Saya buatkan untuk awak.

93
00:06:25,949 --> 00:06:27,122
Oh, okey.

94
00:06:30,170 --> 00:06:30,967
Jadi?

95
00:06:31,681 --> 00:06:33,254
Macam mana hubungan kamu?

96
00:06:34,992 --> 00:06:37,164
- Okey je.
- Baguslah.

97
00:06:37,631 --> 00:06:39,623
Saya tengok kamu berdua bertukar surat dah lama.

98
00:06:39,779 --> 00:06:41,185
Mesti ada perkembangan.

99
00:06:41,961 --> 00:06:42,948
Ya.

100
00:06:54,078 --> 00:06:56,122
Dah siap. Koko untuk orang istimewa.

101
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:05,306
Orang istimewa?

102
00:07:05,869 --> 00:07:10,631
Typhoon pelanggan istimewa kafe saya.

103
00:07:13,408 --> 00:07:14,770
Saya cuma datang ambil sesuatu.

104
00:07:15,118 --> 00:07:18,880
- Dia dah hantar hari ni?
- Oh, ya. Dia dah hantar.

105
00:07:20,339 --> 00:07:23,976
Hari ni kau datang waktu pelik, Fah.

106
00:07:24,167 --> 00:07:26,099
Biasanya aku nampak kau waktu pagi.

107
00:07:27,311 --> 00:07:28,518
Kebetulan aku lapang.

108
00:07:32,011 --> 00:07:33,168
Dan...

109
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,472
Kau dah belanja dia koko?

110
00:07:37,005 --> 00:07:38,093
Uh—

111
00:07:38,665 --> 00:07:41,650
Mestilah. Aku takkan lupa.

112
00:07:44,934 --> 00:07:46,688
Hari ni Phoon belajar dengan kawan-kawan di kafe, kan?

113
00:07:49,619 --> 00:07:51,309
Oh, ya.

114
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:53,229
Kalau macam tu, ikut aku.

115
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,925
Okey.

116
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:00,927
Jom.

117
00:08:13,834 --> 00:08:14,497
Phoon.

118
00:08:16,628 --> 00:08:17,222
Ya?

119
00:08:17,869 --> 00:08:18,841
Apa khabar?

120
00:08:19,737 --> 00:08:21,280
Saya sihat.

121
00:08:21,811 --> 00:08:23,180
P'Fah pula macam mana?

122
00:08:23,601 --> 00:08:24,680
Saya pun sihat.

123
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,226
Kalau ada apa-apa,

124
00:08:27,488 --> 00:08:28,693
awak boleh beritahu saya bila-bila.

125
00:08:34,946 --> 00:08:36,656
Saya tak lulus peperiksaan kemasukan sekolah perubatan.

126
00:08:37,671 --> 00:08:38,586
Maaf.

127
00:08:39,595 --> 00:08:40,594
Kenapa awak minta maaf?

128
00:08:41,528 --> 00:08:43,171
Maksud saya, awak dah bersusah payah bimbing saya.

129
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,383
Awak okey?

130
00:08:48,081 --> 00:08:49,906
Mula-mula saya agak kecewa.

131
00:08:50,044 --> 00:08:55,097
Tapi sekarang saya rasa mungkin ini yang terbaik.

132
00:08:55,835 --> 00:08:56,720
Kenapa pula?

133
00:08:57,745 --> 00:09:00,133
Saya rasa saya akan ambil peperiksaan kemasukan fakulti yang saya suka.

134
00:09:03,647 --> 00:09:07,990
Saya baru buat keputusan penting, walaupun saya tak boleh cakap apa.

135
00:09:08,115 --> 00:09:11,462
Tapi bila fikir pasal awak, saya jadi lebih berani.

136
00:09:14,445 --> 00:09:15,417
Hebatnya.

137
00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:17,545
Terima kasih.

138
00:09:44,998 --> 00:09:47,333
Terima kasih sebab tolong semalam.

139
00:09:48,517 --> 00:09:50,320
Awak dah ucap terima kasih semalam.

140
00:09:51,016 --> 00:09:52,294
P'Fah...

141
00:09:52,416 --> 00:09:53,634
Awak pun ingat.

142
00:09:53,841 --> 00:09:55,863
Yang saya takut guruh.

143
00:09:56,660 --> 00:09:57,995
Dan takut gelap.

144
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,903
Mestilah saya ingat.

145
00:10:00,890 --> 00:10:02,314
Bila elektrik terputus,

146
00:10:02,788 --> 00:10:06,007
yang saya fikir dulu, "Macam mana Phoon?"

147
00:10:06,402 --> 00:10:07,437
"Phoon dekat mana?"

148
00:10:07,797 --> 00:10:09,482
Bila saya sedar awak ke tandas,

149
00:10:09,608 --> 00:10:11,053
saya terus pergi cari awak.

150
00:10:11,674 --> 00:10:12,546
P'Fah...

151
00:10:13,954 --> 00:10:15,094
Sepanjang setahun ni,

152
00:10:16,416 --> 00:10:17,915
saya dah banyak matang.

153
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:21,216
Saya tahu.

154
00:10:21,851 --> 00:10:22,933
Awak buat dengan sangat baik.

155
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,856
Awak tak nak tanya saya?

156
00:10:26,302 --> 00:10:27,568
Tentang kenapa dulu saya...

157
00:10:27,877 --> 00:10:29,114
Awak nak cerita pada saya?

158
00:10:34,577 --> 00:10:36,222
Kalau tak nak, tak perlu.

159
00:10:36,561 --> 00:10:37,792
Saya percaya

160
00:10:38,357 --> 00:10:39,939
awak mesti ada sebab awak.

161
00:10:40,090 --> 00:10:41,042
Bila awak dah bersedia,

162
00:10:41,202 --> 00:10:42,312
awak boleh beritahu saya.

163
00:10:43,616 --> 00:10:45,096
Saya...

164
00:10:46,792 --> 00:10:49,165
Saya takut awak masih marah.

165
00:10:51,336 --> 00:10:53,136
Saya tak marah pada awak.

166
00:10:54,611 --> 00:10:55,765
Jangan fikir sangat.

167
00:11:03,994 --> 00:11:07,669
Baju ni cantik, tapi longgar. Saya tak boleh pakai.

168
00:11:11,785 --> 00:11:12,770
Kenapa?

169
00:11:13,848 --> 00:11:15,463
Saya cuma terfikir...

170
00:11:27,411 --> 00:11:28,882
Awak memang kecil.

171
00:11:39,908 --> 00:11:41,155
Dengan P'Fah, mungkin...

172
00:11:41,491 --> 00:11:45,785
- Kembali macam dulu.
- Macam dulu?

173
00:11:46,725 --> 00:11:49,180
Maksud aku, semalam P'Fah...

174
00:11:49,314 --> 00:11:51,600
tepuk kepala aku dan cakap,

175
00:11:51,783 --> 00:11:53,825
"Awak memang kecil."

176
00:11:54,225 --> 00:11:57,401
Tunggu, "kecil" tu maksudnya "rendah" je, kan?

177
00:11:58,782 --> 00:12:00,857
North, kenapa rosakkan suasana?

178
00:12:01,047 --> 00:12:04,613
Dia maksudkan manja, bodoh. Serius.

179
00:12:05,454 --> 00:12:08,585
Apa pun, fokus pada "tepuk kepala" tu.

180
00:12:08,734 --> 00:12:09,795
Kenapa dengan itu?

181
00:12:11,564 --> 00:12:12,151
Hei.

182
00:12:12,957 --> 00:12:14,510
Kenapa muka kau macam tu?

183
00:12:16,407 --> 00:12:20,752
Aku tipu P'Fah pasal Fun.

184
00:12:22,213 --> 00:12:24,915
Kalau dia tahu, dia mesti marah.

185
00:12:25,238 --> 00:12:26,426
Jadi kau nak beritahu dia

186
00:12:26,797 --> 00:12:29,551
pasal P'Fun?

187
00:12:30,881 --> 00:12:33,075
Aku cuma tak nak menipu lagi.

188
00:12:34,745 --> 00:12:37,080
Aku rasa itu bagus. Bila kau jumpa dia,

189
00:12:37,570 --> 00:12:39,502
kau boleh minta maaf lagi.

190
00:12:39,789 --> 00:12:40,918
Aku rasa semuanya okey.

191
00:12:41,733 --> 00:12:43,075
Lagipun kau ikhlas.

192
00:12:43,682 --> 00:12:45,032
Rasanya itu yang aku akan buat.

193
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,631
Hei, korang.

194
00:12:50,011 --> 00:12:51,130
Hari ni,

195
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,690
jom pergi baca surat.

196
00:12:53,103 --> 00:12:54,727
Dao, ikut kami.

197
00:12:55,038 --> 00:12:57,872
Tak, aku ada kerja.

198
00:12:59,607 --> 00:13:03,110
- Aku pun dulu susah, tapi tak ambil kerja macam tu.
- Tak kerja? Dulu kau buat.

199
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:07,288
Yalah. Kau je terserempak P'Jo. Tu je nasib kau.

200
00:13:07,921 --> 00:13:10,752
Yalah, yalah. Kepala kau yang serabut sekarang.

201
00:13:14,336 --> 00:13:15,109
Nah.

202
00:13:16,945 --> 00:13:18,161
Aku tengah pilih lagi.

203
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,248
Apa kena-mengena dengan kau?

204
00:13:21,379 --> 00:13:22,592
Hei, bagi aku tengok juga.

205
00:13:24,995 --> 00:13:26,140
North, jangan tolak. Tepi.

206
00:13:26,628 --> 00:13:28,054
Bagi aku tengok. Kenapa kedekut sangat?

207
00:13:29,106 --> 00:13:31,488
Wah.

208
00:13:31,666 --> 00:13:33,167
Itu gambar matahari ke?

209
00:13:34,047 --> 00:13:34,882
Ini--

210
00:13:35,133 --> 00:13:39,071
Bukan ni langit Phoon ke?

211
00:13:39,202 --> 00:13:42,648
– North, berhenti. Kau melampau.
– Kenapa kau halang aku?

212
00:13:42,807 --> 00:13:44,037
Tengoklah perangai kau tu.

213
00:13:44,241 --> 00:13:47,231
– Cepat makan sebelum P'Fah nampak.
– Ya, cepat.

214
00:13:48,164 --> 00:13:50,180
Cepat makan. P'Fah nak datang.

215
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:52,682
Nak lagi? Nah, ambil.

216
00:13:52,997 --> 00:13:54,364
Habiskan semua.

217
00:13:54,989 --> 00:13:55,964
Semua sekali.

218
00:13:59,905 --> 00:14:02,085
– Kau yang mula.
– Aku bukan budak suruhan.

219
00:14:03,865 --> 00:14:07,325
– Bye, P'Gib! Bye!
– Bye!

220
00:14:07,386 --> 00:14:09,484
Esok aku datang ambil kupon baru.

221
00:14:09,859 --> 00:14:11,931
Kupon kafe aku dah nak habis.

222
00:14:26,385 --> 00:14:27,340
Fah.

223
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:30,940
Dua hari ni kau datang waktu petang.

224
00:14:31,066 --> 00:14:33,171
Kau sengaja tunggu ke?

225
00:14:33,736 --> 00:14:34,509
Tak.

226
00:14:34,797 --> 00:14:36,392
Aku nak dia balik dulu.

227
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:37,722
Supaya kami tak terserempak.

228
00:14:37,965 --> 00:14:39,613
Okey, tunggu sekejap.

229
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:40,503
Okey.

230
00:14:44,828 --> 00:14:45,466
Nah, ini.

231
00:14:46,219 --> 00:14:47,890
Kenapa tak datang pagi macam biasa?

232
00:14:48,438 --> 00:14:50,700
Aku nak ambil seseorang dalam perjalanan.

233
00:14:52,068 --> 00:14:53,653
Tak ada apa. Aku pergi dulu.

234
00:14:58,357 --> 00:14:59,349
Ambil seseorang?

235
00:15:01,868 --> 00:15:02,826
Nak sikit?

236
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,290
P'Hill, nak sikit?

237
00:15:19,917 --> 00:15:22,053
Hei, Fah. Malam ni nak makan apa?

238
00:15:22,574 --> 00:15:23,451
Tak tahu.

239
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:26,550
Korang langsung tak membantu.

240
00:15:28,131 --> 00:15:29,493
Pergi tanya isteri kau.

241
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,902
Tadi aku nampak dia berkeliaran sini.

242
00:15:32,385 --> 00:15:33,625
Dia pergi tandas.

243
00:15:38,429 --> 00:15:39,700
North mungkin manjakan Ter.

244
00:15:40,282 --> 00:15:41,217
Aku?

245
00:15:41,745 --> 00:15:42,417
Ish.

246
00:15:43,041 --> 00:15:45,060
Aku tak nak bergaduh dengan North.

247
00:15:46,737 --> 00:15:48,401
Kalau macam tu, sushi pun okey.

248
00:15:48,761 --> 00:15:51,208
– Kedai mana?
– Yang depan kampus tu?

249
00:15:51,327 --> 00:15:53,994
Baru buka. Review kata sedap sangat.

250
00:15:54,681 --> 00:15:55,537
Bunyi bagus. Jom.

251
00:15:56,244 --> 00:15:58,448
Korang pergi dulu. Aku tunggu North.

252
00:16:00,988 --> 00:16:02,177
Phoon, ikut kami.

253
00:16:03,521 --> 00:16:04,789
Awak boleh ikut saya.

254
00:16:10,891 --> 00:16:12,475
Kalau macam tu, aku ikut P'Fah.

255
00:16:13,093 --> 00:16:15,007
Baik. Jumpa di restoran.

256
00:16:16,454 --> 00:16:17,211
Cepat.

257
00:16:18,635 --> 00:16:19,669
Jom. Jumpa nanti.

258
00:16:19,851 --> 00:16:21,074
– Saya tolong bawakan.
– Jumpa di restoran.

259
00:16:21,309 --> 00:16:22,672
Oh, terima kasih.

260
00:16:24,622 --> 00:16:25,469
Pergilah.

261
00:16:25,795 --> 00:16:27,484
– Nak sikit?
– Tak.

262
00:16:42,365 --> 00:16:43,284
Terima kasih.

263
00:16:56,897 --> 00:16:59,342
Phoon, boleh ambil beg kertas biru tu?

264
00:17:12,026 --> 00:17:12,690
Err...

265
00:17:14,906 --> 00:17:16,598
Boleh keluarkan barang dalam tu?

266
00:17:21,962 --> 00:17:23,348
Apa yang ada dalam tu?

267
00:17:30,272 --> 00:17:31,120
Gambar.

268
00:17:31,595 --> 00:17:34,368
Surat dan snek sikit.

269
00:17:36,528 --> 00:17:37,429
Gambar apa?

270
00:17:37,817 --> 00:17:39,285
Bunga.

271
00:17:40,776 --> 00:17:44,315
Boleh bacakan surat tu untuk saya?

272
00:17:45,687 --> 00:17:47,485
Err... boleh ke?

273
00:17:47,761 --> 00:17:48,539
Ya.

274
00:17:48,774 --> 00:17:52,635
Saya nak tahu isinya, tapi saya memandu.

275
00:17:52,924 --> 00:17:54,862
Boleh bacakan untuk saya?

276
00:18:04,448 --> 00:18:10,893
Bunga yang saya jaga berbulan-bulan akhirnya mekar.

277
00:18:11,309 --> 00:18:12,688
Cantik sangat.

278
00:18:13,524 --> 00:18:16,220
Saya tak tahan, jadi ambil gambar untuk kongsi.

279
00:18:17,201 --> 00:18:20,005
Kalau awak berminat nak tanam,

280
00:18:21,466 --> 00:18:23,291
saya gembira nak cadangkan caranya.

281
00:18:25,248 --> 00:18:29,367
Peperiksaan akhir dah dekat, awak mesti kuat belajar.

282
00:18:29,927 --> 00:18:31,573
Saya pun sama.

283
00:18:32,318 --> 00:18:35,454
Teruskan ya.

284
00:18:35,948 --> 00:18:38,734
Jom harungi peperiksaan akhir sama-sama.

285
00:18:43,561 --> 00:18:44,364
Itu saja?

286
00:19:11,930 --> 00:19:13,257
Er, P’Fah.

287
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:17,337
Bukan kita nak makan sushi dengan yang lain?

288
00:19:19,629 --> 00:19:20,811
Tempat ni sedap.

289
00:19:21,358 --> 00:19:22,562
Saya nak P’Fah cuba.

290
00:19:23,931 --> 00:19:25,780
Oh.

291
00:19:30,724 --> 00:19:31,782
Okey.

292
00:19:48,391 --> 00:19:48,992
Nah.

293
00:20:01,583 --> 00:20:02,632
P’Fah.

294
00:20:03,807 --> 00:20:04,191
Ya?

295
00:20:05,358 --> 00:20:08,207
Kalau saya mula semula sebagai pelajar tahun pertama,

296
00:20:08,765 --> 00:20:09,832
adakah itu membazir masa?

297
00:20:15,032 --> 00:20:15,934
Tak.

298
00:20:16,312 --> 00:20:18,425
Kalau itu buat awak lebih kenal diri sendiri,

299
00:20:18,863 --> 00:20:20,120
dan tahu apa yang awak betul-betul nak belajar.

300
00:20:20,657 --> 00:20:21,637
Apa yang awak suka.

301
00:20:22,269 --> 00:20:24,235
Apa pun, saya rasa ia berbaloi.

302
00:20:28,482 --> 00:20:29,234
Jadi—

303
00:20:29,524 --> 00:20:30,915
awak nak pindah fakulti mana?

304
00:20:31,161 --> 00:20:32,090
Dah putuskan?

305
00:20:33,308 --> 00:20:34,703
Saya nak belajar fotografi.

306
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:36,282
Baguslah.

307
00:20:37,365 --> 00:20:38,632
Lagipun awak memang suka.

308
00:20:41,466 --> 00:20:42,300
Oh ya—

309
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:44,185
fakulti tu—

310
00:20:44,567 --> 00:20:46,942
bukan perlukan markah aliran Seni–Bahasa?

311
00:20:47,875 --> 00:20:49,567
Awak dah lama buat persediaan?

312
00:20:50,306 --> 00:20:51,045
Err—

313
00:20:51,322 --> 00:20:52,552
Saya baru mula belajar.

314
00:20:53,082 --> 00:20:53,825
Tapi—

315
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,998
Saya takut tak sempat ingat semua.

316
00:21:05,785 --> 00:21:06,746
Phoon...

317
00:21:08,389 --> 00:21:10,385
Nak saya jadi tutor awak?

318
00:21:13,118 --> 00:21:14,290
Betul-betul tak apa ke?

319
00:21:16,869 --> 00:21:17,807
Mestilah.

320
00:21:20,327 --> 00:21:21,611
Tapi kali ni—

321
00:21:22,668 --> 00:21:24,223
saya takkan bagi awak lari ke mana-mana.

322
00:21:29,598 --> 00:21:30,841
Kalau macam tu—

323
00:21:31,019 --> 00:21:32,324
saya serahkan pada P’Fah, ya.

324
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:35,477
Boleh.

325
00:21:41,045 --> 00:21:41,734
Terima kasih.

326
00:21:52,045 --> 00:21:53,349
Pasal—

327
00:21:55,482 --> 00:21:56,431
surat tu—

328
00:21:58,961 --> 00:21:59,700
ya?

329
00:22:04,733 --> 00:22:06,362
Awak boleh tanya. Kenapa?

330
00:22:10,669 --> 00:22:12,232
Surat tu daripada siapa?

331
00:22:17,075 --> 00:22:17,850
Saya tak tahu.

332
00:22:18,537 --> 00:22:20,862
Dah berhubung, tapi awak tak tahu dia siapa?

333
00:22:26,094 --> 00:22:26,968
Ya.

334
00:22:27,709 --> 00:22:29,740
Saya hampir tak tahu apa-apa pasal dia.

335
00:22:31,300 --> 00:22:33,922
Dia tak cerita apa-apa pasal diri dia?

336
00:22:34,579 --> 00:22:35,437
Tak.

337
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:37,481
Saya tanya, tapi dia tak nak cakap.

338
00:22:38,728 --> 00:22:39,377
Sayangnya.

339
00:22:40,149 --> 00:22:42,186
Tapi tak apa, betul.

340
00:22:42,576 --> 00:22:43,902
Kalau dia selesa—

341
00:22:44,534 --> 00:22:46,228
saya okey dengan apa saja.

342
00:22:49,718 --> 00:22:50,724
Dan—

343
00:22:51,656 --> 00:22:53,118
dah berapa lama awak berhubung?

344
00:22:54,493 --> 00:22:55,743
Dalam—

345
00:22:56,143 --> 00:22:57,355
lebih kurang dua bulan.

346
00:22:58,992 --> 00:22:59,746
Hmm—

347
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:01,167
lama juga.

348
00:23:05,623 --> 00:23:06,896
Sebenarnya,

349
00:23:07,189 --> 00:23:08,973
saya nak terus berhubung lagi lama.

350
00:23:20,444 --> 00:23:21,251
Baguslah.

351
00:23:21,628 --> 00:23:22,208
Hmm?

352
00:23:23,065 --> 00:23:23,819
Apa yang bagus?

353
00:23:25,324 --> 00:23:26,084
Oh—

354
00:23:26,496 --> 00:23:27,586
Maksud saya—

355
00:23:27,961 --> 00:23:29,782
orang yang—

356
00:23:30,308 --> 00:23:31,545
tulis surat tu.

357
00:23:31,933 --> 00:23:33,072
Dia macam comel.

358
00:23:33,525 --> 00:23:34,397
Tapi—

359
00:23:34,548 --> 00:23:36,368
sekarang ni tak ramai orang—

360
00:23:36,974 --> 00:23:38,995
guna surat untuk berhubung lagi.

361
00:23:39,182 --> 00:23:40,053
Mm.

362
00:23:41,663 --> 00:23:44,404
Tapi ada juga kekurangannya.

363
00:23:45,075 --> 00:23:46,459
Bila awak nak jumpa—

364
00:23:47,032 --> 00:23:48,579
awak tak boleh.

365
00:23:49,448 --> 00:23:50,982
Bila awak nak dengar suara dia—

366
00:23:51,402 --> 00:23:52,429
awak tak boleh.

367
00:23:54,134 --> 00:23:55,352
Lagi satu—

368
00:23:56,331 --> 00:23:57,915
kalau satu hari dia hilang—

369
00:23:58,317 --> 00:23:59,182
saya—

370
00:23:59,662 --> 00:24:01,210
tak tahu nak buat apa.

371
00:24:06,365 --> 00:24:07,696
Kalau dia betul-betul hilang—

372
00:24:08,568 --> 00:24:10,208
kejam juga dia, kan?

373
00:24:14,573 --> 00:24:15,697
Kejam?

374
00:24:18,085 --> 00:24:19,160
Mestilah.

375
00:24:19,557 --> 00:24:21,420
Lepas buat orang suka dia sampai macam ni—

376
00:24:21,629 --> 00:24:22,942
lepas tu hilang begitu saja.

377
00:24:23,448 --> 00:24:24,890
Kalau itu bukan kejam—

378
00:24:25,105 --> 00:24:26,254
apa lagi nak panggil?

379
00:24:27,605 --> 00:24:29,939
Orang patut belajar bertanggungjawab atas perasaan orang lain.

380
00:24:32,448 --> 00:24:33,198
Betul tak?

381
00:25:31,865 --> 00:25:32,765
Fun.

382
00:25:33,222 --> 00:25:35,208
Saya betul-betul gembira dapat hari ni.

383
00:25:36,145 --> 00:25:39,967
Dulu saya ingat hidup saya dah tak bermakna—

384
00:25:40,247 --> 00:25:41,494
bila Fun tak ada di sisi saya.

385
00:25:42,928 --> 00:25:44,088
Tapi akhirnya—

386
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:45,727
saya dapat jumpa semua orang.

387
00:25:45,976 --> 00:25:47,733
Saya belajar banyak benda.

388
00:25:48,197 --> 00:25:50,380
Dan dari situ saya sedar, hidup—

389
00:25:50,851 --> 00:25:52,019
dah pun perkara paling baik.

390
00:25:53,225 --> 00:25:55,530
Dulu saya ingat hujan takkan berhenti.

391
00:25:56,506 --> 00:25:58,194
Tapi bila ia akhirnya berhenti—

392
00:25:58,958 --> 00:26:00,857
langit memang cantik sangat.

393
00:26:01,835 --> 00:26:03,330
Berbaloi tunggu.

394
00:26:05,362 --> 00:26:07,075
Menunggu langit yang lebih cerah.

395
00:26:31,708 --> 00:26:34,168
Maksudnya, awak tahu P’Fah suka dia,

396
00:26:34,502 --> 00:26:36,091
tapi orang yang tulis surat tu belum tahu.

397
00:26:37,814 --> 00:26:39,100
Jadi awak nak buat apa?

398
00:26:39,776 --> 00:26:41,370
Terus hantar surat macam ni?

399
00:26:42,044 --> 00:26:42,988
Saya rasa itu saja caranya, ya.

400
00:26:43,792 --> 00:26:45,185
Kita dah sampai sejauh ni.

401
00:26:45,866 --> 00:26:48,586
Dan P’Fah pun dah cakap dia suka dia.

402
00:26:52,214 --> 00:26:55,597
Saya gembira rancangan surat jadi untuk Maew.

403
00:26:55,891 --> 00:26:56,832
Jadi?

404
00:26:58,885 --> 00:26:59,712
Saya, betul ke?

405
00:27:00,641 --> 00:27:03,708
Maew, dah sejauh ni—yakinlah sikit dengan diri.

406
00:27:03,891 --> 00:27:10,068
- Awak dah nak ajak dia jadi teman lelaki. Eh, kenapa pukul aku?
- Dia malu.

407
00:27:10,245 --> 00:27:12,188
Wah, merah betul muka kau.

408
00:27:12,626 --> 00:27:14,500
Kantoi.

409
00:27:14,845 --> 00:27:17,173
Tapi serius, P’Fah bukan main-main.

410
00:27:17,659 --> 00:27:18,841
Dia pun jelas pasal tu.

411
00:27:21,327 --> 00:27:22,213
Hei, korang.

412
00:27:22,589 --> 00:27:23,822
Aku ada benda nak cakap.

413
00:27:24,161 --> 00:27:24,711
Hmm?

414
00:27:33,154 --> 00:27:35,577
- Aku nak berhenti belajar.
- Apa? Kau ada batu karang?

415
00:27:35,709 --> 00:27:36,685
Berhenti belajar.

416
00:27:36,949 --> 00:27:39,400
Seriuslah, kau tak pernah serius masa yang betul.

417
00:27:39,500 --> 00:27:40,183
Aku ingat kau cakap batu karang.

418
00:27:41,493 --> 00:27:42,545
Kau betul-betul nak berhenti?

419
00:27:43,085 --> 00:27:43,933
Ya.

420
00:27:44,308 --> 00:27:46,642
Aku dah mohon peperiksaan fotografi.

421
00:27:49,429 --> 00:27:51,438
Jadi tinggal aku dengan Foam je.

422
00:27:52,208 --> 00:27:54,065
Kalau tinggal korang berdua, jangan bergaduh, okey?

423
00:27:55,386 --> 00:27:58,345
- Ya.
- Tapi aku sedih sikit.

424
00:27:59,072 --> 00:28:00,881
Aku takkan bersama korang lagi.

425
00:28:03,471 --> 00:28:06,737
Alah, drama sangat.

426
00:28:06,954 --> 00:28:08,478
Kita tetap akan jumpa juga, kan?

427
00:28:08,952 --> 00:28:10,198
- Ya.
- Betul.

428
00:28:11,968 --> 00:28:13,782
Kami betul-betul gembira untuk kau, Maew.

429
00:28:14,072 --> 00:28:16,082
Sebab kau akhirnya pilih jalan kau sendiri.

430
00:28:21,211 --> 00:28:23,112
Ayah kau takkan cakap apa-apa?

431
00:28:23,647 --> 00:28:25,696
Lagi-lagi sekarang kau dah cakap dgn P'Fah.

432
00:28:28,085 --> 00:28:29,518
Apa jadi, jadilah.

433
00:28:31,429 --> 00:28:32,296
Hmm...

434
00:28:32,817 --> 00:28:34,730
Kalau ayah tak nak bayar aku belajar fotografi,

435
00:28:35,404 --> 00:28:39,379
aku buat fotografi bebas saja, atau apa-apa.

436
00:28:41,764 --> 00:28:43,665
Aku pun tak nak bergantung pada dia selamanya.

437
00:28:46,457 --> 00:28:47,973
Tak apa. Kau ada kami.

438
00:28:48,434 --> 00:28:49,657
Jangan tekan diri sangat.

439
00:28:50,499 --> 00:28:53,005
Kau dah hebat sebab berani buat keputusan ni.

440
00:28:54,767 --> 00:28:57,040
Ya, aku pun rasa aku memang hebat.

441
00:28:57,561 --> 00:28:59,214
Sebab aku lahir,

442
00:28:59,687 --> 00:29:00,740
dan sebab semua hal pasal Fun.

443
00:29:02,663 --> 00:29:06,958
Setiap kali ayah salahkan aku, padahal aku tak buat salah.

444
00:29:09,128 --> 00:29:12,604
Dulu aku fikir kalau satu hari aku hilang mak dan Fun,

445
00:29:13,034 --> 00:29:14,551
aku tak nak hilang ayah juga.

446
00:29:15,105 --> 00:29:18,131
Sampailah aku mula hilang diri sendiri.

447
00:29:20,980 --> 00:29:22,635
Gila, kacaknya.

448
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:40,271
Hei.

449
00:29:40,908 --> 00:29:42,481
Daotok, nak pergi makan?

450
00:29:42,831 --> 00:29:45,602
Tak, aku nak balik bilik buat kerja.

451
00:29:46,185 --> 00:29:47,020
Tengoklah dia.

452
00:29:47,208 --> 00:29:47,936
Wah.

453
00:29:48,395 --> 00:29:50,303
Asyik tinggal kawan je.

454
00:29:51,017 --> 00:29:52,902
Kau tahu tak sunyinya kami?

455
00:29:52,924 --> 00:29:56,349
- Betul.
- Aku nampak korang makan dgn teman lelaki tiap hari.

456
00:29:56,560 --> 00:29:57,869
Bila masa korang sempat sunyi?

457
00:30:00,008 --> 00:30:01,657
Wah, pandai betul kau cakap.

458
00:30:02,025 --> 00:30:06,579
Aku tahu—korang makan diam-diam, korang berdua dgn P'Fah, kan?

459
00:30:07,186 --> 00:30:07,921
Ya.

460
00:30:08,400 --> 00:30:11,703
Hari tu aku order banyak sushi. Lepas tu kau suruh aku habiskan.

461
00:30:11,802 --> 00:30:13,259
Betul. Dia mesti yang bayar.

462
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:20,136
Jadi sekarang Typhoon dgn P'Fah dah baik semula,

463
00:30:20,511 --> 00:30:23,371
macam mana hal orang surat tu?

464
00:30:24,757 --> 00:30:26,552
- Jawab.
- Okeylah.

465
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:28,536
Kantoi.

466
00:30:29,142 --> 00:30:30,337
“Okeylah” tu maksudnya apa?

467
00:30:35,026 --> 00:30:38,085
Kau betul-betul tak nak beritahu P'Fah?

468
00:30:39,588 --> 00:30:44,051
Aku takut kalau aku cakap, P'Fah akan kecewa.

469
00:30:44,194 --> 00:30:44,893
Hei.

470
00:30:45,256 --> 00:30:46,219
Tak mungkin.

471
00:30:46,666 --> 00:30:47,807
Tapi kita tak tahu, kan?

472
00:30:48,841 --> 00:30:50,598
Aku rasa P'Fah takkan kecewa.

473
00:30:51,045 --> 00:30:53,822
P'Fah nampak macam suka orang dalam surat tu, Phoon.

474
00:30:53,927 --> 00:30:55,208
Ya.

475
00:30:55,471 --> 00:30:56,517
Aku pun rasa macam tu.

476
00:30:56,752 --> 00:30:59,699
Terima kasih. Aku rasa lega. Aku percaya Dao.

477
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:02,245
Hei, aku pun cakap benda sama.

478
00:31:02,674 --> 00:31:03,925
- Kenapa kau tak percaya aku?
- Hah?

479
00:31:04,494 --> 00:31:06,605
Alah, jomlah.

480
00:31:06,776 --> 00:31:08,641
Kau tak pernah percaya apa aku cakap.

481
00:31:08,994 --> 00:31:10,063
Kau merepek apa ni?

482
00:33:01,117 --> 00:33:04,395
Boleh tak kalau aku nak jumpa kau sekali je?

483
00:33:21,318 --> 00:33:22,853
Kau rasa Phoon akan datang jumpa kau?

484
00:33:24,355 --> 00:33:25,122
Dia akan datang.

485
00:33:25,348 --> 00:33:26,768
Kenapa kau yakin sangat?

486
00:33:30,644 --> 00:33:31,736
Kau ada rancangan apa?

487
00:33:39,188 --> 00:33:40,477
Pasal surat tu...

488
00:33:41,228 --> 00:33:43,629
Sebenarnya, aku pun ada benda yang aku tak pasti.

489
00:33:45,808 --> 00:33:46,625
Apa dia?

490
00:33:47,527 --> 00:33:52,508
Aku tak pasti orang tu betul-betul suka aku atau tak.

491
00:33:53,515 --> 00:33:56,324
Kalau dia tak suka kau, kenapa dia tulis surat?

492
00:33:56,711 --> 00:33:57,875
Aku tak tahu.

493
00:33:58,090 --> 00:34:01,075
- Mungkin dia tulis pada ramai orang.
- Tak mungkin.

494
00:34:01,579 --> 00:34:02,685
Macam mana kau tahu, Phoon?

495
00:34:07,087 --> 00:34:08,056
Aku agak je.

496
00:34:10,936 --> 00:34:14,242
Jadi maksudnya dia suka aku, kan?

497
00:34:14,533 --> 00:34:15,171
Ya.

498
00:34:20,948 --> 00:34:22,096
Aku je, kan?

499
00:34:26,536 --> 00:34:26,983
Ya.

500
00:34:27,845 --> 00:34:31,902
Jadi dia akan sayang aku je, kan?

501
00:34:38,628 --> 00:34:39,614
Kau cakap apa?

502
00:34:41,530 --> 00:34:45,260
Ya. Aku pasti dia akan sayang P'Fah, P'Fah saja.

503
00:34:45,546 --> 00:34:46,186
Oh.

504
00:34:56,288 --> 00:34:57,502
Seronok usik dia?

505
00:34:58,936 --> 00:35:00,213
Dia comel juga bila kena usik.

506
00:35:01,703 --> 00:35:02,608
Tengok kawan kau tu.

507
00:35:04,448 --> 00:35:05,771
Tapi bila fikir betul-betul,

508
00:35:05,994 --> 00:35:07,749
North dengan Ter taklah teruk mana pun.

509
00:35:08,085 --> 00:35:09,297
Mereka memang backup kawan mereka.

510
00:35:09,659 --> 00:35:10,847
Walaupun tak berapa lancar.

511
00:35:13,474 --> 00:35:14,842
Jadi kau rasa kita patut buat apa?

512
00:35:17,325 --> 00:35:19,213
Aku rasa Ter memang akan ikut Phoon je.

513
00:35:20,337 --> 00:35:21,651
Dia mungkin akan pujuk Phoon.

514
00:35:22,722 --> 00:35:24,480
Tapi North pula,

515
00:35:24,967 --> 00:35:26,180
dia yang akan paksa dia datang.

516
00:35:31,002 --> 00:35:33,810
Sebab tu aku yakin Phoon akan datang—sebab North.

517
00:35:34,431 --> 00:35:36,518
Hei, kau patut ucap terima kasih pada aku.

518
00:35:37,031 --> 00:35:38,442
Isteri aku buat sampai macam ni untuk kau, tau.

519
00:35:39,681 --> 00:35:42,471
- Okey.
- Teman lelaki kau buat baik, kau pula ambil kredit semua.

520
00:35:42,622 --> 00:35:43,520
Mestilah.

521
00:35:55,952 --> 00:35:57,096
Korang tengah cakap pasal apa?

522
00:35:58,844 --> 00:36:00,253
Bising gila.

523
00:36:08,524 --> 00:36:11,082
Dan kau ni kenapa? Kenapa muka kau macam Jo?

524
00:36:12,257 --> 00:36:13,952
Mana ada dia macam aku?

525
00:36:14,813 --> 00:36:17,908
Kau selalu sengih bila ada rancangan nakal, macam—

526
00:36:19,997 --> 00:36:21,543
macam “gila, aku kacak” ke apa.

527
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,437
Yang—

528
00:36:27,211 --> 00:36:29,414
kau memang kacak pun, Jo.

529
00:36:31,416 --> 00:36:32,580
Maksud aku,

530
00:36:33,386 --> 00:36:36,645
dalam dunia ni, kau je aku mengaku aku nombor dua.

531
00:36:36,902 --> 00:36:39,222
Yang lain semua, aku rasa aku lagi hensem.

532
00:36:40,189 --> 00:36:41,121
Pandai cover.

533
00:36:45,469 --> 00:36:46,865
Tak ke terkeluar sikit?

534
00:36:47,183 --> 00:36:48,235
Kau nampak macam mak remaja.

535
00:36:48,367 --> 00:36:49,512
Kempiskan perut sikit.

536
00:36:51,890 --> 00:36:54,053
Ini memang tahap paling padu.

537
00:36:54,554 --> 00:36:56,930
Serius, korang buat apa ni?

538
00:36:57,404 --> 00:36:58,152
Menyamar dia.

539
00:36:58,771 --> 00:37:01,303
Aku tahu ini penyamaran, tapi untuk apa?

540
00:37:01,674 --> 00:37:02,948
Cakap je terus dengan dia.

541
00:37:03,691 --> 00:37:05,949
Maew tak berani jumpa dia terus, North.

542
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:08,991
Jadi korang betul-betul nak menyamar macam ni?

543
00:37:09,263 --> 00:37:11,168
- Ya.
- Kau ingat P'Fah tak perasan?

544
00:37:12,957 --> 00:37:14,620
Hei, tengok ni.

545
00:37:15,091 --> 00:37:15,891
Yang ni.

546
00:37:16,605 --> 00:37:17,382
Macam mana?

547
00:37:17,709 --> 00:37:20,602
Kalau terserempak, kau takkan cam dia.

548
00:37:20,752 --> 00:37:22,602
Tak cam? Bodoh. Tengoklah dia tu.

549
00:37:23,204 --> 00:37:25,422
Sial, North. Kalau kau tak cam, jangan berlagak pandai.

550
00:37:25,687 --> 00:37:28,171
Kau tak tolong, siap menyusahkan lagi. Serius.

551
00:37:28,423 --> 00:37:31,882
Dah, dah. Jangan gaduh. Berhenti.

552
00:37:32,668 --> 00:37:33,976
Jadi, baju ni lepas tak?

553
00:37:35,328 --> 00:37:36,477
Mm, lepas.

554
00:37:36,576 --> 00:37:37,989
Aku rasa lepas juga.

555
00:37:38,376 --> 00:37:40,136
Tapi baik buka. Panas.

556
00:37:40,211 --> 00:37:40,840
Ya.

557
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:41,685
Okey?

558
00:37:41,912 --> 00:37:43,100
Nanti hari sebenar kau pengsan.

559
00:37:44,776 --> 00:37:45,702
Aduh, aduh.

560
00:37:47,014 --> 00:37:47,933
Aku rasa aku boleh tahan.

561
00:37:50,568 --> 00:37:52,302
Berdiri dalam bilik pun kau dah tercungap.

562
00:37:52,509 --> 00:37:56,677
Tapi P'Fah cam suara Maew.
Jadi korang tak boleh cakap langsung?

563
00:37:58,888 --> 00:37:59,853
Kalau macam tu, macam mana kalau—

564
00:38:00,325 --> 00:38:01,317
Aku tulis dalam buku nota?

565
00:38:02,567 --> 00:38:03,334
Boleh.

566
00:38:03,656 --> 00:38:05,442
Aku rasa dia tak kisah sangat.

567
00:38:09,154 --> 00:38:12,746
Jadi kau dah balas, setuju nak jumpa?

568
00:38:15,536 --> 00:38:16,431
Belum.

569
00:38:16,865 --> 00:38:18,290
Aku tak tahu nak cakap apa.

570
00:38:21,311 --> 00:38:23,850
Cakap je kau nak jumpa, tapi ada syarat.

571
00:38:24,334 --> 00:38:25,311
Tapi sekarang,

572
00:38:25,917 --> 00:38:28,011
Aku rasa P'Fah dah tergila-gila kat kau.

573
00:38:28,939 --> 00:38:30,204
Apa pun kau minta, dia mungkin setuju je.

574
00:38:33,026 --> 00:38:34,835
Dah kantoi.

575
00:38:36,823 --> 00:38:37,708
North.

576
00:38:40,770 --> 00:38:41,622
Aku lagi.

577
00:38:45,579 --> 00:38:47,299
Terima kasih sebab nak jumpa aku.

578
00:38:47,742 --> 00:38:49,642
Aku pun nak jumpa kau.

579
00:38:50,229 --> 00:38:51,899
Mungkin nampak agak rumit,

580
00:38:52,404 --> 00:38:54,145
tapi aku ada beberapa syarat.

581
00:39:08,731 --> 00:39:09,965
Tempat ni ke?

582
00:39:15,754 --> 00:39:17,091
Hei, kenapa kau tegang sangat?

583
00:39:17,533 --> 00:39:18,245
Jom.

584
00:39:23,034 --> 00:39:23,851
Satu.

585
00:39:24,349 --> 00:39:26,860
Aku akan pakai sesuatu yang pelik masa jumpa kau.

586
00:39:27,197 --> 00:39:28,946
Tolong jangan kisah.

587
00:39:55,786 --> 00:39:56,628
Dua.

588
00:39:57,459 --> 00:40:00,059
Aku tak nak kau cuba tahu siapa aku.

589
00:40:07,434 --> 00:40:08,794
Terima kasih sebab datang jumpa aku.

590
00:40:12,170 --> 00:40:14,845
Tiga. Kalau kau terjumpa tahu

591
00:40:14,961 --> 00:40:16,078
siapa aku,

592
00:40:17,459 --> 00:40:18,844
tolong buat-buat tak tahu.

593
00:40:23,625 --> 00:40:25,425
Banyak benda aku nak cerita pada kau.

594
00:40:31,528 --> 00:40:32,925
Aku rasa tenang sangat.

595
00:40:35,983 --> 00:40:37,717
Kau zon selamat aku.

596
00:40:40,284 --> 00:40:41,182
Boleh?

597
00:40:42,059 --> 00:40:43,820
Boleh jadi zon selamat aku?

598
00:40:56,291 --> 00:40:58,757
Aku boleh jadi apa saja.

599
00:40:59,454 --> 00:41:00,490
Manisnya.

600
00:41:01,029 --> 00:41:02,946
Kenapa kau baik sangat dengan aku?

601
00:41:11,245 --> 00:41:14,085
Sebab kau penting bagi aku.

602
00:41:16,394 --> 00:41:18,179
Aku memang nak dengar kau cakap macam tu.

603
00:41:27,383 --> 00:41:29,601
Kau penting bagi aku.

604
00:41:30,691 --> 00:41:32,275
Kau belum bersedia lagi, kan?

605
00:41:43,032 --> 00:41:44,137
Maaf.

606
00:41:44,764 --> 00:41:45,688
Tak apa.

607
00:41:46,805 --> 00:41:47,976
Buat masa ni,

608
00:41:48,244 --> 00:41:49,574
ini dah cukup.

609
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,000
Pernah tak orang cakap

610
00:41:56,468 --> 00:41:57,637
kau comel sangat?

611
00:42:00,979 --> 00:42:03,333
Selama ni kau kat mana?

612
00:42:18,337 --> 00:42:20,001
Ada benda aku nak tanya kau.

613
00:42:27,010 --> 00:42:27,731
Ya?

614
00:42:28,915 --> 00:42:30,617
Aku pernah tulis dalam surat aku yang

615
00:42:30,851 --> 00:42:32,200
nama Tonfah tu datang daripada

616
00:42:32,389 --> 00:42:34,117
ayah aku nak aku jadi langit,

617
00:42:34,333 --> 00:42:36,299
dan mak aku nak aku jadi pokok.

618
00:42:36,845 --> 00:42:37,605
Kau pula?

619
00:42:38,075 --> 00:42:39,228
Kau nak aku jadi apa?

620
00:42:48,351 --> 00:42:49,330
Cinta.

621
00:43:04,668 --> 00:43:07,029
Kenapa kau nak jumpa aku?

622
00:43:10,081 --> 00:43:13,822
Aku cuma nak tahu apa aku rasa bila jumpa kau.

623
00:43:14,377 --> 00:43:15,682
Lepas tu aku sedar

624
00:43:16,189 --> 00:43:17,475
rasa dia memang sedap.

625
00:43:19,773 --> 00:43:21,185
Aku nak jumpa kau selalu.

626
00:43:22,737 --> 00:43:23,718
Kau pula?

627
00:43:24,721 --> 00:43:26,600
Kenapa kau putuskan nak datang jumpa aku?

628
00:43:32,537 --> 00:43:34,420
Sebab kau kata kau nak jumpa aku.

629
00:43:38,044 --> 00:43:38,930
Kenapa?

630
00:43:39,595 --> 00:43:42,088
Walaupun kau pilih nak sorok identiti sampai macam ni.

631
00:43:50,174 --> 00:43:52,983
Aku pun tak pasti. Kau cuma kata nak jumpa aku,

632
00:43:53,271 --> 00:43:54,760
jadi aku pun nak datang jumpa kau.

633
00:43:57,850 --> 00:43:59,675
Boleh aku pegang tangan kau?

634
00:44:13,155 --> 00:44:14,762
Kau pun cinta bagi aku.

635
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:20,552
Kenapa?

636
00:44:25,810 --> 00:44:27,995
Kau tak suka? Maaf.

637
00:44:34,920 --> 00:44:38,223
Nak lap air mata dulu? Aku pejam mata, okey?

638
00:44:58,908 --> 00:45:00,296
Dah berhenti menangis?

639
00:45:18,545 --> 00:45:19,506
Tak apa.

640
00:46:06,001 --> 00:46:06,869
Tunggu.

641
00:46:14,872 --> 00:46:16,514
Aku suka sangat bibir kau yang lembut

642
00:46:17,149 --> 00:46:18,232
bila aku cium kau.

643
00:47:05,462 --> 00:47:07,631
Apa pun, kali pertama kau jumpa—

644
00:47:09,640 --> 00:47:10,571
Jangan cakap.

645
00:47:10,755 --> 00:47:12,278
Lama betul kita tak jumpa, P'Fah.

646
00:47:12,714 --> 00:47:14,813
Bukan semalam kita baru jumpa?

647
00:47:17,031 --> 00:47:18,096
Malam ni kau lapang?

648
00:47:18,471 --> 00:47:20,045
Aku akan tutor kau.

649
00:47:20,746 --> 00:47:22,515
Peluang dah ada. Pergi buat.

650
00:47:22,992 --> 00:47:24,225
P'Fah baik dengan semua orang.

651
00:47:24,989 --> 00:47:27,894
Dia mungkin betul-betul suka orang dari surat tu.

652
00:47:28,161 --> 00:47:31,048
Kau mungkin tertanya kenapa aku cium kau.

653
00:47:33,459 --> 00:47:35,023
Jawapannya ialah—

